{"tid":1688633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日約16:20 Sogo外有手足被拉入黨鐵站後即落閘","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T15:42:18.000Z","uid":25951,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdc684a039910ff61ffa49210bdd66867d5f505","tid":1688633,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"發夢今日大約16:40行到去sogo出面(銅鑼灣E出口對出)遇到一班銀髮族, 佢地同我講:<br />\n大約15分鐘前(我諗around 16:20-25)有5個黑衫後生企左係E出口, 比d防暴拉左入黨鐵站, 跟住班狗即刻落閘, d阿叔係度搖個閘都冇用, 有兩個女仔係度喊, 好似係因為被拉入去既係佢地朋友<br />\n<br />\n佢地影唔到相, 我當時都唔見佢話喊果兩個女仔,<br />\n我叫左佢地係第個入口落大堂睇下會唔會等到d狗拉手足返狗屋<br />\n<br />\n當時銅鑼灣黨鐵站只係封左某d出口, 我相信如果班狗拉左手足落大堂再拉入控制室應該會有人見到, 聽銀髮族講果陣大堂本身都有十幾個後生...<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家傳出去搵返果幾位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後一定要提醒全世界: 發夢唔好企係黨鐵出口附近呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a3c2bd02157dfbb013e7bad50fb7b27cda22463a","tid":1688633,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"甴曱平"},{"pid":"d9d00ea7bcdd7beab55ab173c204148122e280e2","tid":1688633,"uid":244529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曱甴王 甴近平"},{"pid":"7bfe897a09a5bf78ce329275beb576a0699ce206","tid":1688633,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"甴曱平"},{"pid":"e573c0910a1238c06cd66ff9483e0a3559ee7d82","tid":1688633,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"甴曱平"},{"pid":"f96476f1d95ea16f6cdcd30a7b0f2ec25df77191","tid":168